  "name": "News: Purchase Order Unit Discounts feature",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"news-purchase-order-unit-discounts-feature\">News: Purchase Order Unit Discounts feature</h1>\n<p>With the release of version 3.13.7, we have implemented the ability to add a unit discount when creating a Purchase Order. Discounts are entered against the items on the order, with the pricing flowing through to the Stock Receipt. </p>\n<p>This is just the start of exciting additions coming up to Purchase Orders.</p>\n<p>Currently Retail Express is working on a dedicated Supplier Returns feature, designed to greatly improve the process required to receive Supplier credits and return stock. </p>\n<p><strong>How it works:</strong></p>\n<ol><li>When adding a product to a Purchase Order users will be able to enter a Unit Discount - the amount discounted <em>per product </em>e.g. A $50 product purchased for $45 instead is a $5 unit discount<br/><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4401957154959/mceclip1.png\" alt=\"mceclip1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4401957154959/mceclip1.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4401957154959/mceclip1.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4401957154959/mceclip1.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4401957154959/mceclip1.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4401957154959/mceclip1.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4401957154959/mceclip1.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4401957154959/mceclip1.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/></li><li>Retail Express will calculate the Purchase Order total using the discounted price</li><li>When receiving the PO the discount will map through to the full Stock Receipt<br/><div><br/><strong>Note:</strong> In the Quick Stock Receipt method no costs are displayed - the user will just need to enter the Supplier Invoice</div><br/><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4401964670991/mceclip2.png\" alt=\"mceclip2.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4401964670991/mceclip2.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4401964670991/mceclip2.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4401964670991/mceclip2.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4401964670991/mceclip2.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4401964670991/mceclip2.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4401964670991/mceclip2.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4401964670991/mceclip2.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/></li></ol><p>The Purchase Order Unit Discount feature is available to use with Franchise Connect and APIs. </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>",
